  /// recommended compaction strategy for most use cases.
  /// </li>
  /// <li>
  /// <code>sort</code>: Organizes data based on specified columns which are
  /// sorted hierarchically during compaction, improving query performance for
  /// filtered operations. This strategy is recommended when your queries
  /// frequently filter on specific columns. To use this strategy, you must first
  /// define a sort order in your Iceberg table properties using the
  /// <code>sort_order</code> table property.
